12 SECTION 7. A NEW SECTION OF SUBTITLE 13 OF KRS CHAPTER 286
13 IS CREATED TO READ AS FOLLOWS:
14 (1) As used in this section, "United States dollar equivalent of virtual currency"
15 means the equivalent value of virtual currency in United States dollars shown on
16 a virtual currency exchange based in the United States for a particular date or
17 period.
