22 person is required to have a license:
23 (a) Directly or indirectly employ any scheme, device, or artifice to defraud or
24 mislead, when the applicant, licensee, or person should have known that the
25 scheme, device, or artifice was defrauding or misleading; or
26 (b) Engage in any:
27 1. Unfair or deceptive practice; or
