1 2. Other act or conduct that would warrant the denial, suspension, or
2 revocation of a license under Section 21 of this Act;
3 (2) Negligently make any false statement, or knowingly or willfully make any
4 omission of material fact, in connection with:
5 (a)_ Any information or reports relating to virtual currency kiosk business in
6 this state filed with:
7 1. A state or federal government agency;
8 2. The registry, as defined in Section 4 of this Act; or
9 3. Any agency or authority, as part of a nationwide licensing system, that
