11 this Act; or
12 (b) Any investigation or examination conducted by the commissioner or any
13 other state or federal government agency relating to virtual currency kiosk
14 business in this state; or
15 (3) Fail to truthfully account for any assets in connection with any virtual currency
16 kiosk transaction in this state.
