4 all other applicable state and federal laws, including all administrative
5 regulations, rules, and orders promulgated, issued, or entered thereunder.
6 (2) (a) A licensee shall use blockchain analytics software to assist in the prevention
7 of sending purchased virtual currency from the licensee to a digital wallet
8 known to be affiliated with fraudulent activity at the time of a transaction.
