4 commissioner and a hearing, a court of competent jurisdiction determines
5 that the commissioner would not be prejudiced by disclosure of the
6 document, material, report, or information.
7 (2) (a) The commissioner shall not be required to testify in any civil action
8 concerning any document, material, report, or information that is
9 confidential under subsection (1) of this section.
10 (b) Any person who received documents, materials, reports, or other
