17 SECTION 19. A NEW SECTION OF SUBTITLE 13 OF KRS CHAPTER 286
18 IS CREATED TO READ AS FOLLOWS:
19 (1) By July 1 of each year, the commissioner shall submit a written report on the
20 licensing of virtual currency kiosk businesses in Kentucky to the Legislative
21 Research Commission for referral to the Interim Joint Committee on Banking
22 and Insurance.
23 (2) The written report required under subsection (1) of this section shall contain, at a
24 minimum, the following information, by calendar year:
25 (a) The number of applications made for a license;
26 (b) The number of applicants who have a license to engage in money
27 transmission;
